### Criar nova jornada
# POST /jornadas → Cria uma nova jornada com os cards vinculados
# 
# Requer header: X-User-Id
# Response esperado (200): JornadaDTO
# 
# A rota substitui as perguntas (cards) vinculadas automaticamente

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

POST {{baseUrl}}/jornadas
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user123

{
  "id": "jornada-react-basics",
  "nome": "React Basics",
  "ativa": true,
  "ordem": 1,
  "createdAt": 1720209591000,
  "updatedAt": 1720209591000,
  "cardIds": ["card-001", "card-002", "card-003"]
}
